Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.29,0:24:08.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril is shot down,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.30,0:24:11.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,and forced to make\N an emergency landing
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.55,0:24:13.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,on the Argentine base ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.09,0:24:15.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time, on Simoun:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.43,0:24:18.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla.
